metadata.name: Summer Seaside Strawberry Splash
metadata.description:
It's Part 1 of our Splash into Summer! 
Meet Felicity our friend who is always ready for adventure and games!

Have a refreshing Seaside Splash of Sweet Strawberry goodness. A little sun, a little sand and sea, and maybe a water gun duel to the death! Well...at least winner gets to pick the lunch spot today hehe ^-^  
Make a splash into the sweetness of summer! Ready Set GO!
